channel.description: I downloaded my Keldagrim Client, even tho It wont connect to my Source. I got a cleaned Project Insanity Source with Netty ! I followed a Tutorial 'How to connect Keldagrim Client with PI', but it says to edit the file 'RS2LoginProtocolDetector' , although I only have RS2LoginProtocol and RS2LoginDetector.. May someone help me ? And also, it has nothing to do with the IP.
